onologue théâtral, poème, extrait de roman, chanson...d'une vingtaine de lignes environ) que vous aurez appris par cœur.</span></div></span><br style="color: rgb(75, 79, 86); font-family: &quot;SF Optimized&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, system-ui, &quot;.SFNSText-Regular&quot;, sans-serif; letter-spacing: -0.12px;"><span style="color: rgb(75, 79, 86); font-family: &quot;SF Optimized&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, system-ui, &quot;.SFNSText-Regular&quot;, sans-serif; letter-spacing: -0.12px;">Horaires : de 9h30 à 17h&nbsp;</span><br style="color: rgb(75, 79, 86); font-family: &quot;SF Optimized&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, system-ui, &quot;.SFNSText-Regular&quot;, sans-serif; letter-spacing: -0.12px;"><span style="color: rgb(75, 79, 86); font-family: &quot;SF Optimized&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, system-ui, &quot;.SFNSText-Regular&quot;, sans-serif; letter-spacing: -0.12px;">Intervenante : Maud Roussel</span><br style="color: rgb(75, 79, 86); font-family: &quot;SF Optimized&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, system-ui, &quot;.SFNSText-Regular&quot;, sans-serif; letter-spacing: -0.12px;"><br style="color: rgb(75, 79, 86); font-family: &quot;SF Optimized&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, system-ui, &quot;.SFNSText-Regular&quot;, sans-serif; letter-spacing: -0.12px;"><span style="color: rgb(75, 79, 86); font-family: &quot;SF Optimized&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, system-ui, &quot;.SFNSText-Regular&quot;, sans-serif; letter-spacing: -0.12px;">Tarifs : 95€ non adhérent*&nbsp;</span><span class="text_exposed_show" style="display: inline; font-family: &quot;SF Optimized&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, system-ui, &quot;.SFNSText-Regular&quot;, sans-serif; color: rgb(75, 79, 86); letter-spacing: -0.12px;"><br>85€ adhérent<br>*comprend 10€ d'adhésion à l'association Le C.I.D.<br><br>Infos et réservations auprès de Melody :&nbsp;<br>lecid.diff@gmail.com / 06 88 55 16 10</span><br></p>		</p>
